div.p:
Finally, I want to convey to the Department the excellent cooperation I received
                    from all members of the U.S. delegation, particularly Meeker, Reis, Helman (State Department);
                    Thacher (USUN); Sohier (NASA); Graybeal (ACTA [ACDA]); Moroncew (ACTA [ACDA]);
                    and Captain Cole (DOD).
